{"an1.198:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 1 ","an1.198:0.2":"15. Dutiyavagga ","an1.198:1.1":"“Etadaggam, bhikkhave, mama savakanam bhikkhunam manomayam kayam abhinimminantanam yadidam culapanthako. ","an1.199:1.1":"… Cetovivattakusalanam yadidam culapanthako. ","an1.200:1.1":"… Sannavivattakusalanam yadidam mahapanthako. ","an1.201:1.1":"… Aranaviharinam yadidam subhuti. ","an1.202:1.1":"… Dakkhineyyanam yadidam subhuti. ","an1.203:1.1":"… Arannakanam yadidam revato khadiravaniyo. ","an1.204:1.1":"… Jhayinam yadidam kankharevato. ","an1.205:1.1":"… Araddhaviriyanam yadidam sono koliviso. ","an1.206:1.1":"… Kalyanavakkarananam yadidam sono kutikanno. ","an1.207:1.1":"… Labhinam yadidam sivali. ","an1.208:1.1":"… Saddhadhimuttanam yadidam vakkali”ti. ","an1.208:1.2":"Vaggo dutiyo. "}